Class Board

  • java.lang.Object
    • Board

  • public class Board
extends java.lang.Object
    Backend that contains the board representation, handles turns while telling GUI to update based on the changed board Also handles AI moves

      • dropToken

        public void dropToken(int colNum)
        Drops the token in the given column for the given player

        Breaks early and does not add token to board if the column is full, or when the game is over.

        Parameters:
        colNum - column number
